China looked at the Italian and yelled. "It's your call, Italy!!"


"No! I can't!" Italy exclaimed, his hands trembling in front of a large grandfather clock.


=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=*=


Is he going to break the clock?
Is he going back in time?


