Romano punched the wall beside him. "That asshole! He got himself killed!"


Japan's eyes widened. "Oh, no! England and the others!"


"Italy, you have to decide now!" China urged.


Italy looked at them with a tear-stained face. "I..."


"You can't, non? Oh, bon, I guess I'll have to go and give them a hand..." France called over as he began walking down the stairs.


